<item>
            <title>[LU-125] conf_sanity leaves lustre in a mounted state on completion, probably due to a call to check_and_cleanup_lustre missing from the end.</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-125</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;conf_sanity leaves lustre in a mounted state on completion, probably due to a call to check_and_cleanup_lustre missing from the end.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Every other test appears to have a call to check_and_cleanup_lustre at the end - conf-sanity does not.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;While fixing this issue it the other tests should be checked to ensure they do include a call to check_and_cleanup_lustre.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
